Licensee wishes to obtain an exclusive Licensed Patent and non-exclusive Licensed Trademarks under the Patents to make and sell it for a commercial use.

Both parties want to define in this Agreement the specific terms and conditions that will apply to Licensee’s use of Licensed Products. 

